Eternal rivals Gor Mahia and AFC Leopards face-off in the first instalment of the Mashemeji derby in the 2018/2019 SportPesa Premier League. This will be the 90th meeting between the two giants, with Gor Mahia aiming at moving into third place in the standings, while Leopards will be seeking to bounce back to winning ways after woeful outings against Bandari and Mount Kenya United saw Ingwe drop to 15th. Follow the live action here.  